---
title: Cal Smart 'Poke' Tilapia Crunch Bowls with Wild Rice and Spicy Mayo Drizzle
description: This calorie-smart spin on a poke bowl features seared tilapia tossed in miso sauce. It's topped with crispy shallots and a spicy mayo drizzle to give it some serious pizzazz!
